---
type: item
item: minecolonies/build_goggles
---
The Builder's Goggles are a helmet-slot item that lets you see what nearby structures will look like when they are finished being built or upgraded.

## Using the Builder's Goggles

Simply wear the Builder's Goggles in your helmet slot. Any structures that are currently under construction or queued for construction nearby will appear as a ghost of their completed form, giving you a preview of how they will look when your {% worker name="builder" /%} is done.
